  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à SBC</title>

    <para>
      The <application>SBC</application> is a digital audio encoder et decoder used to
      transfer data to Bluetooth audio output devices like headphones or loudspeakers.
    </para>

    &lfs72_checked;

